exibility to its levels. Keep in mind the movements that will happen when the balls collide and plan your strategy accordingly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master conveyor belt mechanics that will move your ball in certain directions. These conveyor belt boxes have their own timelines, so you will have to carefully plan how they affect your sequence of actions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861120/extras/606045c284d6fca0d45f7518665c4d00.poster.avif?t=1753173946\" width=604 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861120/extras/606045c284d6fca0d45f7518665c4d00.webm?t=1753173946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861120/extras/606045c284d6fca0d45f7518665c4d00.mp4?t=1753173946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enjoy 200+ Levels</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy more than 200+ levels where you will be tested. Line Time doesn’t feature filler levels: once you learn the basic mechanics, you will face real challenges immediately.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861120/extras/1bcb8cc34b695032d3091cf79e08523f.poster.avif?t=1753173946\" width=604 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861120/extras/1bcb8cc34b695032d3091cf79e08523f.webm?t=1753173946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861120/extras/1bcb8cc34b695032d3091cf79e08523f.mp4?t=1753173946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
